    <item>
      <title>由于债务稳步上升，惠誉将中国前景下调至负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将中国长期外债前景从稳定调整为负面，理由是中国公共财政前景面临的风险不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三月份通胀数据将延长美联储降息时间的戏剧性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/march-inflation-data-to-prolong-drama-around-fed-rate-cut-timing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三公布的消费者物价月度报告不太可能解决围绕美联储降息时机的争论，预测人士预计，在年初通胀数据上升后，降息会有所放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/march-inflation-data-to-prolong-drama-around-fed-rate-cut-timing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
