    <item>
      <title>新西兰维持基准利率 5.50%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/new-zealand-maintains-benchmark-interest-rate-at-5-50-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如彭博社调查的所有 25 名经济学家所预期的那样，新西兰央行将主要利率稳定在 5.50%。伊冯·曼和大卫·英格尔斯在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/new-zealand-maintains-benchmark-interest-rate-at-5-50-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰维持利率不变，认为持续需要紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/new-zealand-holds-rates-sees-ongoing-need-for-tight-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行连续第六次会议维持利率不变，并表示需要在一段时间内保持高利率，以确保通胀得到抑制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/new-zealand-holds-rates-sees-ongoing-need-for-tight-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告显示美国库存增加，油价连续两天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份行业报告指出美国原油库存增加后，油价连续两天下跌，尽管中东紧张局势不断升温以及欧佩克+持续实施的限制措施预计将限制跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 23:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
